function clamp(x,y,z) return(math.min(z,math.max(y,x))) end
-- https://open.spotify.com/track/5LHd7HZD2JmTND0Z6QRcB5 --among us
tgX=property.getNumber("Deviation tgt X") or 0 tgY=property.getNumber("Deviation tgt Y") or 0
function onTick() lst_X=input.getNumber(5) lst_Y=input.getNumber(6) roll=input.getNumber(7)
dist=input.getNumber(3) speed=input.getNumber(4) if input.getBool(1) then oX,oY= math.sin(math.atan(input.getNumber(1))-math.atan(lst_X))*dist-tgX, -math.sin(math.atan(input.getNumber(2))-math.atan(lst_Y))*dist-tgY dir=math.atan(oX,oY)+roll dist=math.sqrt(oX^2+oY^2) X=math.sin(dir)*dist Y=math.cos(dir)*dist dX,dY=(X-oldX)*60,(Y-oldY)*60 if abs(dX)<50 then iX=clamp(iX+X,-.6,.6) elseif abs(X)>50 then iX=0 end if abs(dY)<50 then iY=clamp(iY+Y,-.6,.6) elseif abs(Y)>50 then iY=trim end output.setNumber(1,clamp(X_o*(clamp(-X,-50,50) * Px - dX * Dx - iX * Iy),-1,1)) output.setNumber(2,clamp(Y_o*(clamp(-Y,-50,50) * Py - dY * Dy - iY * Iy),-1,1)) oldX,oldY=X,Y else X,Y,dX,dY,iX,iY,oldX,oldY=0,0,0,0,0,trim,0,0 output.setNumber(1,0) output.setNumber(2,0) end output.setNumber(3,input.getNumber(3)) output.setNumber(4,speed) end

m=math pi=m.pi tau=pi*2 sin=m.sin cos=m.cos tan=m.tan atan=m.tan
c=property.getNumber("Distance between sensors (m)")
lastdist=0
function onTick() lst_X=atan(input.getNumber(5)) lst_Y=atan(input.getNumber(6))
A=pi/2-atan(input.getNumber(1)) B=pi/2+atan(input.getNumber(2)) C=pi-A-B a=(c/sin(C))*sin(A)
el=(atan(input.getNumber(4))-lst_Y)
dist=a/cos(el) -- correcting distance for elevation, probably unnecessary
output.setNumber(1,dist) output.setNumber(2,(dist-lastdist)*60) -- speed lastdist=dist end
